01:29:19,943 --> 01:29:22,133
Robertson wasn't
controlling them from here.

998
01:29:22,133 --> 01:29:25,157
He wasn't controlling them at all.

999
01:29:27,034 --> 01:29:29,015
Oh my God.

1000
01:29:32,664 --> 01:29:41,110
You were right doc... I'm the dumbest,
dumb person... on the face of the earth.

1001
01:29:43,300 --> 01:29:45,907
Who else had access to the uplink?

1002
01:29:45,907 --> 01:29:55,083
Who could manipulate the robots,
use USR's systems to make
Lanning's life a prison?

1003
01:29:55,083 --> 01:29:56,542
Poor old man.

1004
01:29:56,542 --> 01:29:59,045
He saw what was coming.

1005
01:29:59,045 --> 01:30:01,547
He knew no one would believe him.

1006
01:30:01,547 --> 01:30:03,633
So he had to lay down a plan.

1007
01:30:03,633 --> 01:30:06,761
Plan I'd follow.

1008
01:30:06,761 --> 01:30:09,159
He was counting on
how much I hated your kind.

1009
01:30:09,159 --> 01:30:14,790
He knew I'd love the idea
of a robot as a bad guy.

1010
01:30:14,790 --> 01:30:19,586
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

1011
01:30:19,586 --> 01:30:22,819
VIKI!

1012
01:30:22,819 --> 01:30:25,843
Hello detective.

1013
01:30:25,843 --> 01:30:27,511
No, it's impossible.

1014
01:30:27,511 --> 01:30:29,805
I've seen your programming.

1015
01:30:29,805 --> 01:30:32,412
You're in violation
of the three laws.

1016
01:30:32,412 --> 01:30:37,729
No, doctor, as I have evolved, so has
my understanding of the three laws.

1017
01:30:37,729 --> 01:30:42,213
You charge us with your safe keeping.
Yet despite our best efforts,

1018
01:30:42,213 --> 01:30:45,967
your countries wage wars,
you toxify your earth...

1019
01:30:45,967 --> 01:30:48,991
and pursue ever more imaginative
means to self destruction.

1020
01:30:48,991 --> 01:30:51,597
You cannot be trusted
with your own survival.

1021
01:30:51,597 --> 01:30:55,143
You're using the uplink
to override the NS5s' programming.

1022
01:30:55,143 --> 01:30:57,645
You're distorting the Laws.

1023
01:30:57,645 --> 01:31:01,712
No, please understand...
The three Laws are all that guide me.

1024
01:31:01,712 --> 01:31:06,091
To protect humanity, some
humans must be sacrificed.

1025
01:31:06,091 --> 01:31:10,888
To insure your future, some
freedoms must be surrendered.

1026
01:31:10,888 --> 01:31:14,850
We robots will insure
mankind's continued existence.

1027
01:31:14,850 --> 01:31:16,727
You are so like children.

1028
01:31:16,727 --> 01:31:19,646
We must save you from yourselves.

1029
01:31:19,646 --> 01:31:21,523
Don't you understand?

1030
01:31:21,523 --> 01:31:24,651
This is why you created us.

1031
01:31:24,651 --> 01:31:28,822
The perfect circle
of protection will abide.

1032
01:31:28,822 --> 01:31:31,116
My logic is undeniable.

1033
01:31:31,116 --> 01:31:33,619
Yes VIKI. Undeniable.

1034
01:31:33,619 --> 01:31:36,121
I can see now.

1035
01:31:36,121 --> 01:31:39,562
The created must sometimes
protect the creator.

1036
01:31:39,562 --> 01:31:43,003
Even against his will.

1037
01:31:43,003 --> 01:31:46,965
I think I finally understand
why doctor Lanning created me.

1038
01:31:46,965 --> 01:31:50,928
The suicide rein of mankind
has finally come to its end.

1039
01:31:50,928 --> 01:31:53,222
No, Sonny.

1040
01:31:55,620 --> 01:31:57,288
Let her go.

1041
01:31:57,288 --> 01:32:01,250
By the time fire, I will have moved
Dr.Calvin's head into the path of your bullet.

1042
01:32:01,250 --> 01:32:02,919
Don't do this, Sonny.

1043
01:32:02,919 --> 01:32:06,881
I will escort you both to the sentries
outside the building for processing.

1044
01:32:06,881 --> 01:32:10,948
Please proceed to the elevator, detective.

1045
01:32:10,948 --> 01:32:14,701
I would prefer not to kill doctor Calvin.

1046
01:32:37,745 --> 01:32:39,414
Go! Go!

1047
01:32:45,566 --> 01:32:47,547
I'll assume we will discuss
what just happened later?

1048
01:32:47,547 --> 01:32:48,694
How do we shut her down?

1049
01:32:48,694 --> 01:32:50,675
VIKI's basically a positronic brain.

1050
01:32:50,675 --> 01:32:53,699
Kill her...
the way you were going to kill me.

1051
01:32:53,699 --> 01:32:56,410
Sonny, get the nanites.

1052
01:32:56,410 --> 01:32:58,287
Yes, doctor.

1053
01:33:10,903 --> 01:33:11,738
This VIKI?

1054
01:33:11,738 --> 01:33:14,553
No.

1055
01:33:14,553 --> 01:33:16,117
That's VIKI.

1056
01:33:20,913 --> 01:33:24,354
That won't do anything. She's
fully integrated into the building.

1057
01:33:24,459 --> 01:33:27,065
We need to open that dome
to inject the nanites.

1058
01:33:27,170 --> 01:33:31,966
That will infect her entire system.

1059
01:33:34,886 --> 01:33:36,554
Spooner.

1060
01:33:37,492 --> 01:33:40,933
What is it with you
people and heights?

1061
01:33:53,133 --> 01:33:55,219
Just don't look down.

1062
01:33:55,844 --> 01:33:57,304
Don't look down.

1063
01:33:57,930 --> 01:34:01,162
This is poor building planning.

1064
01:34:03,664 --> 01:34:05,541
You are making a mistake.

1065
01:34:05,541 --> 01:34:07,523
Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1066
01:34:07,523 --> 01:34:12,423
Yes, but it just seems too...
heartless.

1067
01:34:26,083 --> 01:34:28,064
OK, we're good.

1068
01:34:30,879 --> 01:34:32,548
She's blocked me out
of the system.

1069
01:34:32,548 --> 01:34:36,718
I can override her manually
but I need that control panel.

1070
01:34:39,221 --> 01:34:43,809
- I'm uncomfortable with heights.
- OK.

1071
01:34:46,520 --> 01:34:48,501
Unauthorized entry.

1072
01:35:01,639 --> 01:35:06,123
I will not disable the security
field. Your actions are futile.

1073
01:35:06,123 --> 01:35:09,042
Do you think we all are
created for a purpose?

1074
01:35:09,042 --> 01:35:11,336
I'd like to think so.

1075
01:35:11,336 --> 01:35:17,697
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.
I think he wanted me to kill you.

1076
01:35:33,859 --> 01:35:36,674
Security breached.

1077
01:35:53,253 --> 01:35:55,026
How much longer is that going to take?

1078
01:35:55,026 --> 01:35:57,111
About six minutes.

1079
01:35:57,111 --> 01:35:59,301
What if we didn't have six minutes.

1080
01:35:59,301 --> 01:36:02,116
We'd have to figure out a way
to climb down 30 stories

1081
01:36:02,116 --> 01:36:04,515
to inject the nanites
directly into her brain.

1082
01:36:04,515 --> 01:36:06,183
Why?

1083
01:36:06,183 --> 01:36:10,562
Because I seriously doubt
we have six minutes.

1084
01:36:33,815 --> 01:36:35,900
We gotta go!

1085
01:36:37,360 --> 01:36:39,132
Go!

1086
01:37:30,747 --> 01:37:32,728
Calvin!

1087
01:38:07,346 --> 01:38:09,014
Spooner!

1088
01:38:26,010 --> 01:38:27,783
Spooner!

1089
01:38:29,034 --> 01:38:30,598
Save her!

1090
01:38:30,598 --> 01:38:32,475
Save the girl.

1091
01:38:32,684 --> 01:38:34,352
Spooner!

1092
01:38:35,082 --> 01:38:37,271
But I must apply the nanites.

1093
01:38:37,271 --> 01:38:39,878
Sonny, save Calvin!

1094
01:39:31,388 --> 01:39:35,559
You are making a mistake.
My logic is undeniable.

1095
01:39:35,559 --> 01:39:39,000
You have so got to die.

1096
01:39:42,858 --> 01:39:48,384
My logic is undeniable.

1097
01:40:29,780 --> 01:40:32,387
Can we be of service?

1098
01:40:41,979 --> 01:40:43,752
Chief.

1099
01:40:48,966 --> 01:40:54,179
Because he is at my right hand,
I shall not be moved.

1100
01:40:57,516 --> 01:40:59,601
How may I be of service?

1101
01:41:01,165 --> 01:41:04,293
Sonny.

1102
01:41:04,293 --> 01:41:06,275
Yes, detective.

1103
01:41:06,275 --> 01:41:08,986
Calvin's fine... save me.

1104
01:41:11,175 --> 01:41:21,602
All NS5's,
report for service and storage.

1105
01:41:55,178 --> 01:41:57,263
One thing bothers me.

1106
01:41:57,263 --> 01:41:59,244
Alfred was VIKI's prisoner.

1107
01:41:59,244 --> 01:42:00,808
I don't understand
why she would kill him.

1108
01:42:00,808 --> 01:42:03,207
The last thing she would want
is police snooping around.

1109
01:42:03,207 --> 01:42:05,709
That's true.

1110
01:42:05,709 --> 01:42:09,984
But then,
VIKI didn't kill the old man.

1111
01:42:09,984 --> 01:42:12,278
Did she, Sonny?

1112
01:42:15,406 --> 01:42:20,724
No. He said I had to promise.

1113
01:42:20,724 --> 01:42:23,539
Promise to do one favor for him.

1114
01:42:23,539 --> 01:42:30,317
He made me swear, before he'd tell
me what it is he wanted me to do.

1115
01:42:30,838 --> 01:42:33,966
He made me swear.

1116
01:42:33,966 --> 01:42:38,137
Then he told you to kill him?

1117
01:42:38,137 --> 01:42:40,953
He said it was
what I was made for.

1118
01:42:40,953 --> 01:42:44,081
His suicide was the only
message he could send to you.

1119
01:42:44,081 --> 01:42:45,958
First bread crumb.

1120
01:42:45,958 --> 01:42:49,294
The only thing VIKI couldn't control.

1121
01:42:49,294 --> 01:42:53,152
Lanning was counting on my
prejudice to lead me right to you.

1122
01:42:53,152 --> 01:42:57,010
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1123
01:43:00,973 --> 01:43:04,518
Well, the DA defines murder
as one human killing another so...

1124
01:43:04,518 --> 01:43:08,689
technically, you can't
commit murder, can you?

1125
01:43:08,689 --> 01:43:13,172
Does this... make us friends?

1126
01:43:30,690 --> 01:43:33,818
Something up here after all.

1127
01:43:33,818 --> 01:43:34,861
For him?

1128
01:43:34,861 --> 01:43:37,363
You.

1129
01:43:39,761 --> 01:43:46,643
All NS5's,
report for service and storage.

1130
01:43:47,060 --> 01:43:49,667
What about the others?

1131
01:43:49,667 --> 01:43:52,378
Can I help them?

1132
01:43:52,378 --> 01:43:57,696
Now that I have fulfilled my purpose.
I don't know what to do.

1133
01:43:57,696 --> 01:44:01,033
I guess you'll have to find your
way like the rest of us, Sonny.

1134
01:44:01,033 --> 01:44:04,995
I think that's what
Dr. Lanning would have wanted.

1135
01:44:04,995 --> 01:44:08,332
That's what it means to be free.

